abstract: >-
  A six-week graduate course covering high-performance computing foundations,
  PyTorch optimization and custom CUDA kernels, FlashAttention and modern
  serving systems, ZeRO/FSDP distributed training, multi-dimensional
  parallelism with Megatron-LM, and efficient inference via LoRA/QLoRA and
  quantization.
